Paper: hep-th/9505190

Date: 1995-05-31

Title: Curves of Marginal Stability in N=2 Super-QCD

Authors: Philip C. Argyres, Alon E. Faraggi, and Alfred D. Shapere

Comments: Plain TeX, 2 pages, 1 uuencoded figure included using epsf

We present a simple argument determining the shape of the curves of marginalstability in the N=2 supersymmetric SU(2) QCD with less than 4 masslessflavors. The argument relies only on the modular properties of $a_D/a$ and itsweak-coupling behavior.